    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sideboards usually for use in the dining room and typically of Italian or Italian-styled designs, generally having two or three cupboard doors and drawers in the frieze area; the bases are often molded and rest directly on the floor or on short feet. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
